Credit Suisse’s Von Bargen to Leave, New York Times Reports

-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 
2011-03-11T05:58:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/credit-suisse-s-von-bargen-to-leave-new-york-times-reports.html
Cristina von Bargen, head of
communications for Credit Suisse’s investment bank and the
Americas, will leave the company, the New York Times reported,
citing an internal memo.  Von Bargen’s departure comes a year after the bank hired
Pamela Thomas-Graham to manage communications, the newspaper
said. Charles Naylor, a spokesman for Credit Suisse, said the
bank was looking for a replacement for von Bargen.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Kraus at 
 jkraus2@bloomberg.net  